creator: Clubmate Limited
descriptionHtml:
Empower anglers to manage their accounts, purchase tickets and renew membership on the go.

Help bailiffs complete their rounds securely, armed with all the tools they need to verify anglers and sell tickets on the spot.

Provide key staff members and volunteers with instant access to member and customer data on any device.

ANGLER ACCESS
The Clubmate app provides anglers with the ability to access and update their profile, manage their memberships, make bookings, purchase tickets, and communicate with their club or fishery.

Note: You must be registered with your fishing club or fishery as a member or customer before using this app.

BAILIFF ACCESS
The Clubmate app provides bailiffs with the ability to verify whether an angler is authorised to fish, check upcoming bookings, validate angler’s details, sell tickets & memberships and add notes to angler’s profiles.

Note: You must be registered as a Bailiff user with your fishing club or fishery before gaining Bailiff access to this app.

ADMIN ACCESS
The Clubmate app provides Staff and Owner users with the ability to access and update member & customer data, communicate with anglers via email, SMS and push notification, sell tickets and memberships, manage upcoming bookings, access financial reporting & member analytics (Owner access only) plus all of the same functionality that a Bailiff can access.

Note: You must be registered as an Owner or Staff user with your fishing club or fishery before gaining Admin access to this app.
